832bf672f0e6d2f718f","tid":195741,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c71443991696457304d8cd3ed96b392bed497bd","tid":195741,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"敢問關於劉細良太平紳士涉偽造訪問《狀元考試考上癮》可以向邊個投訴？<br />\n蘋果、壹週刊及x方都不受理"},{"pid":"d6a5f5643c2d7885b96c8932934a66dab8fb9137","tid":195741,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"點解啲口賤口臭貼就大把人推，呢啲做正經野就冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bebe1fe63e909a3fe45fe9934d639fdd9f1f992","tid":195741,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解啲口賤口臭貼就大把人推，呢啲做正經野就冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登都係社會嘅縮影<br />\n大部分日好似好care民主進程 本土思潮<br />\n但有啲咩花生價值高就係咁討論啲無謂嘢<br />\n唔好怪佢哋 唔好屌佢哋<br />\n屌佢地都冇用 <br />\n做好自己份內事先 總有人會留意同加入一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3a93d5d371ef7e2ea68c31f79c74f8db06080c","tid":195741,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"(DQ多件?) 民建聯立法會議員柯創盛涉虛報學歷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/183346?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/183346?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n已經冇人理"},{"pid":"f077d009166a1209a8eb99daa7afaba151a7ca07","tid":195741,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e91fbef3d37ae8b6e5867ecc666126c6906c8bf","tid":195741,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:04:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7051d434afce12d6f70ab40c84d4ae65af8f62e","tid":195741,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790f263e8eee99c51b608ffe07e56b0d52ec1d8f","tid":195741,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066f2f08dcc8e69b832f81a6472660b8740c9a32","tid":195741,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"135f42d998cac71baa7ab33443a44466bf657573","tid":195741,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實加入建制有無得諗，從内打破。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGood<br />\n不違言，我有幾個中同(80後)<br />\n當年滿腔熱血，不甘封建腐敗<br />\n三大畢業，各司專業 : 教師，律師，會計<br />\n<br />\n卿本佳人，竟然身投建制<br />\n初以為裏應外合，由內擊破<br />\n<br />\n點知越發毒深<br />\n平心理論就話一幣兩面<br />\n辭窮口拙就話你邏輯有誤<br />\n<br />\n佔中佔旺之後更不相往來<br />\n<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"ddd14b9bbf2c96ae8dae8ac63495af8283f519cf","tid":195741,"uid":14482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79783d1839ed05b3e72538ee6b053c1a565a9335","tid":195741,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解啲口賤口臭貼就大把人推，呢啲做正經野就冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人本身鍾意睇口賤嘅人，兩登，fb如是。乜嘢串嘴作家無料都大把人捧。"},{"pid":"c3a343b07017431ebdae087656bd176935444ea8","tid":195741,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"支持呀，依家有互聯網，無咁易收埋啲腐敗嘢。<br />\n人微言輕？有批判思維既人都唔會俾糖衣呃到"}]}